"n.钩子，釦子；紧握 【英】 n. 钩子,釦子(device for fastening things);紧握(firm hold) 【考】 lathe : shape / clasp : fasten(车床使成形/釦子使 固定) 【例】 The clasp of my brooch is broken . n. 扣钩, 釦子(用来将多个物体连在一起); (用扣钩)扣紧; (用双臂紧紧)抱住; 用手(紧握) 【例】My button won'apos;t clasp 我的钮釦钩怎么也扣不上. She clasped my arm with fear 她害怕地握紧了我的手臂. 【记】源于clap(拍手, 拍): 釦子就是把两片布拍在一起. 【类】lathe: shape = clasp: fasten 车床使成形 = 釦子使固定 【记】c=g, l=r，grasp 抓紧；clap是拍，中间有个“丝”，clasp是用丝将两个拍的东西勾在一起 【相关】clap 拍手，clip 夹子，clamp 夹子，夹钳，clasp 紧握 clasp (n.)  c.1300, claspe, ""metal catch or hook used to hold things together,"" perhaps a metathesis of clapse, and thus from or related to Old English clyppan ""clasp"" (see clip (v.2)). clasp (v.)  late 14c., from clasp (n.). Related: Clasped; clasping."
